Natural Born Killers;;81;;49;;R;;Woody Harrelson and Juliette Lewis are two young, attractive serial killers who become tabloid-TV darlings, thanks to a sensationalistic press led by Robert Downey Jr. The press reports the pair as they go on a 52 people killing spree. A controversial look at the way the media portrays criminals.;;Crime,Drama;;Oliver Stone;;1994;;Woody Harrelson,Juliette Lewis,Robert Downey Jr.,Tommy Lee Jones,Tom Sizemore,Rodney Dangerfield,Russell Means,Edie McClurg,Balthazar Getty,Joe Grifasi,O-Lan Jones;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/natural_born_killers